    - CodeSets: Database-managed code/value pairs  
    - Meta Types: Code-managed type definitions (app/core/meta_types.py)
    - Meta Items & Values: Database-managed with unified JSON storage
    
    ğŸ†• LATEST: Term table consolidation and unified JSON storage
    ğŸ—‘ï¸ REMOVED: tx_term_content intermediate table 
    ğŸ—‘ï¸ REMOVED: Legacy multi-column approach (value_json, code_id, taxonomy_term_id)
    ğŸ—‘ï¸ REMOVED: Separate taxonomy term junction table
    âœ… IMPROVED: Merged tx_term and tx_term_content for simpler structure
    âœ… IMPROVED: Direct tx_term â†’ tx_term_version relationship
    âœ… IMPROVED: Single value_json column with complete data enrichment
